  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6773 trading below the 6795 flip strike in a PIN regime, dealers are net long gamma and will mechanically buy this dip while selling any rallies back toward 6800. The massive GEX surge (1390% in 5min) has created an extremely dense wall of positive gamma between 6775-6800, meaning dealers will aggressively dampen volatility and force mean reversion within this 25-point range. Watch for heavy dealer selling if price approaches the 6800 max gamma level, while expecting strong dealer buying support at the 6760 negative gamma pocket.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect tight range-bound action between 6760-6800 with dealers capping moves.",
